Console is a pure-ruby Ruby/SDL based quake-like console intended for inclusion in games.

Requirements
------------
Ruby 1.8.2 or later: http://www.ruby-lang.org
Ruby/SDL 0.9.5 or later: http://www.kmc.gr.jp/~ohai/rubysdl.en.html

Installation
------------
No installation required, just drop it in the directory you would like and include it or install the Gem and add to your app:

require 'rubygems'
require_gem 'Console'

Usage
------
Please see sample.rb for usage.
To add commands just add a method to commands.rb in console/ or make a subclass of Console and add protected methods to it.

Support
-------
Support can be found at http://rubyforums.com or http://rubyforge.org/projects/nebulargauntlet/

